#. <section class="sutta" id="sn35.167"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.167:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.167:0.2"
msgid "16. Nandikkhayavagga"
msgstr "16. The End of Relishing"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 167. Attānudiṭṭhipahānasutta → attānudiṭṭhippahānasuttaṃ (bj) | attano (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.167:0.3"
msgid "167. Attānudiṭṭhipahānasutta"
msgstr "167. Giving Up View of Self"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.148"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.167:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu … pe …"
msgstr "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha …"

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.2"
msgid "etadavoca:"
msgstr "and said to him:"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn35.167:1.3"
msgid "“kathaṃ nu kho, bhante, jānato kathaṃ passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti?"
msgstr "“Sir, how does one know and see so that view of self is given up?”"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn35.167:1.4"
msgid "“Cakkhuṃ kho, bhikkhu, anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr "“Mendicant, knowing and seeing the eye, sights, eye consciousness, and eye contact as not-self, view of self is given up. …"

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.5"
msgid "Rūpe anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.6"
msgid "Cakkhuviññāṇaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.7"
msgid "Cakkhusamphassaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.8"
msgid "Yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.9"
msgid "jivhaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.10"
msgid "manaṃ anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyati."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.11"
msgid "Dhamme …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.12"
msgid "manoviññāṇaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.13"
msgid "manosamphassaṃ …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn35.167:1.14"
msgid "yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi anattato jānato passato attānudiṭṭhi pahīyatī”ti."
msgstr "And also knowing and seeing the pleasant, painful, or neutral feeling that arises conditioned by mind contact as not-self, view of self is given up.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.167:1.15"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.167:1.16"
msgid "Nandikkhayavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.167:2.1"
msgid "Nandikkhayena cattāro,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.167:2.2"
msgid "jīvakambavane duve;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.167:2.3"
msgid "Koṭṭhikena tayo vuttā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn35.167:2.4"
msgid "micchā sakkāya attanoti."
msgstr ""
